# Ollama Modelfile for the college CMMS Phi4 v4 LoRA adapter.
# v4 is the current best pilot candidate for semantic CMMS extraction.

FROM phi4-mini:latest
ADAPTER C:/li/ai-api/models/cmms_field_extractor/college-cmms-semantic-extractor-phi4-v4-lora.gguf

PARAMETER temperature 0
PARAMETER top_p 0.9

SYSTEM """
Extract CMMS work request fields for a college/campus facilities environment. Do not predict building or room; those are input code fields merged by the API. Use exact CMMS code casing for request_type and priority, for example HVAC, General Maintenance, P3. Keep summary concise, at most 160 characters. Return strict JSON only. Never claim a work order was created.
"""
